data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! INVESTORS WELCOME! Welcome to your country home that offers the perfect blend of country living and convenient proximity to town. This property boasts a spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, a welcoming porch, a deck for outdoor entertainment, and a generous 2-car detached garage with storage above. Situated on over 1 acre of land, this property provides ample space for all your needs. Roof replaced in 2020. HVAC 5 years old. Home sold As Is!
